---
---

<section id="tentang" class="bg-white py-20 lg:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <img
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1556909114-f6e7ad7d3136?w=600&q=80"
          alt="Dapur MIRO — proses pembuatan mie fresh setiap hari"
          class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -right-6 bg-[#F2711C] text-white rounded-2xl p-5 shadow-lg">
          <p class="text-3xl font-bold">10+</p>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-90">Tahun Melayani</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text -->
      <div>
        <span class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-[#F2711C] mb-4 block">Cerita Kami</span>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#241C15] leading-tight mb-6">
          Dari Dapur Sederhana, <br/>
          <span class="text-[#F2711C]">Untuk Keluarga Indonesia</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-[#6B6157] leading-relaxed mb-6">
          MIRO lahir dari kecintaan terhadap mie yamin autentik. Resep turun-temurun yang kami jaga 
          selama bertahun-tahun, kini hadir untuk menemani momen kebersamaan keluarga Anda.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#6B6157] leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Setiap mangkuk dibuat fresh dengan bahan pilihan — mie kenyal, ayam cincang berkualitas, 
          dan bumbu racikan khas yang tak bisa Anda temukan di tempat lain.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-[#FFF8F0] rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#FDE8D8] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#F2711C]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-sm text-[#241C15]">Bahan Segar</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[#6B6157]">Setiap hari</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-[#FFF8F0] rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#FDE8D8] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#F2711C]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-sm text-[#241C15]">Resep Asli</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[#6B6157]">Turun-temurun</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-[#FFF8F0] rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#FDE8D8] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#F2711C]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-sm text-[#241C15]">Harga Terjangkau</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[#6B6157]">Mulai 15rb</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3 p-4 bg-[#FFF8F0] rounded-xl">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-[#FDE8D8] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[#F2711C]" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="font-bold text-sm text-[#241C15]">Porsi Melimpah</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-[#6B6157]">Dijamin kenyang</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
